p.k: Granville's scheme to sell salami as an erotically charged new product called Yaggis is in danger as a customer's husband returns seeking redress. Meanwhile, Cyril and Eric need advice on how to impress their wives. (2015). Cast: David Jason, Lynda Baron, James Baxter, Stephanie Cole, Maggie Ollerenshaw, Brigit Forsyth, Johnny Vegas, Kulvinder Ghir, Nina Wadia, Tim Healy. Director: Dewi Humphreys.
